npcText: He is wearing a striped swimsuit, and you can see small droplets of water falling onto his face. His large eyes seem rather unfocused, gazing at nothing in particular.
Charlie: No it's okay... 'm brother will bring one over for me.
Swimmin'! My brother took me to the pool. He said he won't be able to if he gets 'drafted'. I'm not sure what that meanns, though...
Charlie: Well, I was with m' brother... I fell asleep in the pool so he probably brought me here.
Press anywhere after clipping to confirm.
